{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01TcoUuL7dMRE8mkM25GJeXJ","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→# Cinis Terminal Context\n     2→Read this before every task.\n     3→\n     4→## Brand\n     5→- Coal #211A14 — background\n     6→- Hot Pool #FF6644 — PRIMARY accent, all interactive elements\n     7→- Ember #E8321A — RESERVED: delete, overdue, urgent ONLY\n     8→- Ash #F0EAD6 — primary text\n     9→- Char #3E3228 — cards, inputs, surfaces\n    10→- Gold #FFB800 — Pro/subscription only\n    11→- Green #4CAF50 — completed/success only\n    12→- Body: Figtree. Numbers/wordmark: Sora.\n    13→- Wordmark: CINIS, Sora 600, 0.16em, uppercase\n    14→- Tagline: \"Where start meets finished.\"\n    15→- NEVER: Cormorant Garamond, $9.99, \"FocusBuddy\"\n    16→\n    17→## Layout\n    18→- paddingBottom: 80px on all scrollable content (Voice FAB clearance)\n    19→- Content padding: 12px 14px on all tabs\n    20→- Sidebar: width 106px, padding 12px 8px\n    21→- Cards: background Char, border rgba(240,234,214,0.08), radius 12px\n    22→- Inputs: radius 8px, background Char\n    23→\n    24→## DB Column Names (exact)\n    25→profiles: id, full_name, persona_blend (text[]), baseline_profile (text),\n    26→  rolling_memory_summary, subscription_status, ai_interactions_today,\n    27→  current_streak, longest_streak, total_xp, theme_id, push_subscription,\n    28→  push_notifications_enabled, morning_time, midday_time, evening_time,\n    29→  checkin_times (array), onboarding_complete, birthday\n    30→\n    31→tasks: id, user_id, title, completed, archived, scheduled_for,\n    32→  completed_at, due_time, rollover_count, notes, sort_order,\n    33→  starred (boolean), task_type (text), estimated_minutes (integer)\n    34→\n    35→bills: id, user_id, name, amount (numeric), due_day, frequency,\n    36→  category, autopay, notes, auto_task\n    37→\n    38→journal_entries: id, user_id, content, ai_response, mood, created_at\n    39→\n    40→progress_snapshots: id, user_id, snapshot_date, tasks_completed,\n    41→  tasks_added, tasks_rolled, focus_minutes, journal_entries, ai_summary\n    42→\n    43→habits: id, user_id, name, frequency, habit_type ('build'/'break')\n    44→habit_completions: id, habit_id, user_id, completed_at\n    45→\n    46→## Do Not Touch\n    47→- lib/memoryCompression.js\n    48→- lib/rateLimit.js\n    49→- pages/api/stripe/webhook.js\n    50→- lib/supabase.js auth config\n    51→\n    52→## Auth Pattern\n    53→- Plain createClient from @supabase/supabase-js\n    54→- onAuthStateChange fires only on INITIAL_SESSION and SIGNED_IN\n    55→- No getSession(). No callback.js. No @supabase/ssr.\n    56→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_016AACCY39huMRvxZN2Eihwg","session_id":"c92e3624-e3e3-45f1-ae19-e176495ae8ad","uuid":"89e48ed0-ec68-4ecc-9c7b-721627919a59","timestamp":"2026-03-26T12:15:51.885Z"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01QNDLX2d6Qnb7UxuuaKxBLr","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→# FocusBuddy PRIMER\n     2→Updated: March 17, 2026 · Session 9 · ~8 hrs this session · ~70 hrs total\n     3→\n     4→## Score\n     5→6.0/10 → 7.5/10 this session\n     6→\n     7→## What Got Done\n     8→- Paper theme removed entirely ✅\n     9→- Display name save fixed ✅\n    10→- Monthly insight decoupled from weekly ✅\n    11→- Dead space fixed on Focus, Calendar, Progress tabs ✅\n    12→- Baseline profile system built and deployed ✅\n    13→- All 3 users backfilled with coaching profiles ✅\n    14→- Baseline profile injected into checkin.js and journal.js ✅\n    15→- frontend-design skill installed ✅\n    16→\n    17→## Still Broken\n    18→- Check-in dead space — ACCEPTED. Do not attempt to fix again.\n    19→- Finance Insights empty state copy — says wrong thing. Quick fix T2.\n    20→- Timer font in Focus tab — still Playfair. Fix in visual polish pass.\n    21→- Persona voice differentiation — deferred. Do not attempt without fresh strategy.\n    22→\n    23→## Do Not Touch\n    24→- checkin.js persona voice logic — deferred\n    25→- Check-in CSS — accepted behavior, stop iterating\n    26→\n    27→## Next Session Opens With\n    28→1. Read ~/.claude/skills/skills/frontend-design/SKILL.md before touching anything\n    29→2. Fire left extension QC sweep — get baseline score\n    30→3. npm install @phosphor-icons/react — full icon replacement pass\n    31→4. Fix timer font in Focus tab\n    32→5. Fix Finance Insights empty state copy\n    33→6. After visual pass hits 8.0+ — rate limiting on AI endpoints\n    34→\n    35→## Launch Blockers Remaining\n    36→1. Rate limiting on AI endpoints\n    37→2. Stripe subscription gating\n    38→3. App score 8.5/10 — currently 7.5/10\n    39→\n    40→## Target Launch\n    41→April 14, 2026 (soft launch to waitlist)\n    42→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_016AACCY39huMRvxZN2Eihwg","session_id":"c92e3624-e3e3-45f1-ae19-e176495ae8ad","uuid":"19b3928f-b4d5-45d1-9ce1-c55dcbaef9e0","timestamp":"2026-03-26T12:15:51.890Z"}
