{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_016AACCY39huMRvxZN2Eihwg","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Great! I have all the information I need. Let me create a comprehensive summary for you:\n\n## Summary of Key Files\n\n### 1. **TERMINAL_CONTEXT.md** — Brand & Database Schema\nThis is the canonical reference for the \"Cinis\" app (rebranded from FocusBuddy):\n\n**Brand:**\n- Primary accent: Hot Pool #FF6644 (all interactive elements)\n- Background: Coal #211A14\n- Text: Ash #F0EAD6\n- Fonts: Figtree (body) | Sora (numbers/wordmark)\n- Tagline: \"Where start meets finished.\"\n\n**Database Tables & Columns:**\n\n| Table | Key Columns |\n|-------|------------|\n| **profiles** | id, full_name, persona_blend (text[]), baseline_profile (text), rolling_memory_summary, subscription_status, ai_interactions_today, current_streak, longest_streak, total_xp, theme_id, push_subscription, push_notifications_enabled, morning_time, midday_time, evening_time, checkin_times (array), onboarding_complete, birthday |\n| **tasks** | id, user_id, title, completed, archived, scheduled_for, completed_at, due_time, rollover_count, notes, sort_order, starred (boolean), task_type (text), estimated_minutes (integer) |\n| **bills** | id, user_id, name, amount (numeric), due_day, frequency, category, autopay, notes, auto_task |\n| **journal_entries** | id, user_id, content, ai_response, mood, created_at |\n| **progress_snapshots** | id, user_id, snapshot_date, tasks_completed, tasks_added, tasks_rolled, focus_minutes, journal_entries, ai_summary |\n| **habits** | id, user_id, name, frequency, habit_type ('build'/'break') |\n| **habit_completions** | id, habit_id, user_id, completed_at |\n\n---\n\n### 2. **PRIMER.md** — Session Status & Blockers\n- **Current Score:** 7.5/10 (target: 8.5+)\n- **Recent Wins:** Paper theme removed, baseline profile system built, dashboard split (7,242→326 lines)\n- **Known Issues (DO NOT FIX):**\n  - Check-in dead space — ACCEPTED. Stop iterating.\n  - Finance Insights empty state copy — quick fix pending\n  - Timer font in Focus tab — Playfair (should be Sora)\n- **Launch Target:** April 14, 2026\n- **Launch Blockers:**\n  1. Rate limiting on AI endpoints\n  2. Stripe subscription gating\n  3. App score 8.5/10\n\n---\n\n### 3. **lessons.md** — Critical Do-Not-Touch Rules\n**Never Modify:**\n- `lib/memoryCompression.js` — Haiku rolling memory\n- `lib/rateLimit.js` — Rate limiting enforcement\n- `pages/api/stripe/webhook.js` — requires `bodyParser: false`\n- `lib/supabase.js` — Auth config\n- `onAuthStateChange` pattern in dashboard.js\n\n**Auth Pattern:**\n- Plain `createClient` from @supabase/supabase-js with localStorage sessions\n- NO `getSession()` | NO `pages/api/auth/callback.js` | NO `@supabase/ssr`\n- Google OAuth redirects directly to `/dashboard`\n\n**Key Patterns:**\n- Tab files live in `components/tabs/` with 11 tab files + shared.js\n- Each tab receives `{ user, profile }` as props\n- No circular imports (tabs must NOT import from dashboard.js)\n- bills.amount must be `numeric(10,2)` — integers lose decimals\n\n---\n\n### 4. **todo.md** — Active Work Queue\n**P1 Blockers:**\n1. Stripe Pro flip not verified end-to-end (LLC blocks live mode)\n2. Push notification toggle not wired to UI\n\n**P2 Queue:**\n- Solver 3 QC sweep needed\n- VAPID_KEY env var cleanup (delete duplicates)\n- OG meta image + favicon updates\n\n---\n\n### 5. **pages/api/checkin.js** — Check-in API Shape\n\n**POST /api/checkin Request Body:**\n```javascript\n{\n  userId: string (required),\n  checkInType: 'morning' | 'afternoon' | 'evening' | 'next_move' | 'focus' | 'weekly_summary',\n  content?: string, // user message (max 2000 chars)\n  message?: string, // alias for content\n  messages?: Array<{ role, content }>, // conversation continuation\n  timezone?: string, // e.g., 'America/Chicago'\n  tasks?: Array, // client tasks for next_move fast path\n  focusTask?: object, // for focus checkin\n  focusDuration?: number // for focus checkin\n}\n```\n\n**POST /api/checkin Response:**\n```javascript\n{\n  message: string, // AI response text\n  actionsExecuted: Array<{\n    tool: string,\n    taskId?: string,\n    result: 'rescheduled' | 'completed' | 'created' | 'error',\n    updatedTask?: object,\n    error?: string\n  }>\n}\n```\n\n**Special Paths:**\n- **next_move (fast path):** Returns only `{ message: string }` — minimal Claude call, no tools\n- **evening:** Auto-reschedules all pending tasks to tomorrow 9am UTC\n- **Continuation:** Supports multi-turn conversations with tool execution\n\n**AI Tools Available:**\n- `reschedule_task`, `update_task_time`, `complete_task`, `archive_task`\n- `create_task`, `create_alarm`\n- `schedule_morning_checkin`, `add_crew_task`, `get_crew_status`\n- `get_bills`, `add_bill`, `update_bill`\n- `log_spend`, `get_daily_number`\n\n**System Prompt Injected Data:**\n- User's persona_blend (drill_sergeant, coach, hype_person, thinking_partner, strategist, empath)\n- baseline_profile (coaching context)\n- rolling_memory_summary (for Pro users, 6+ message exchanges)\n- Timezone offset (UTC conversion mandatory)\n- Live task list (ID, title, rollover_count, due_time)\n- Bill list with IDs for tool calls\n- Daily budget calculation: (monthly_income - monthly_bills) / 30\n- Crew context (if user has crews)\n\n---\n\n### 6. **pages/dashboard.js** — Main Component Structure\n\n**Architecture:**\n- Single-page app with 11 tabs + sidebar\n- **Sidebar (106px width):** Logo, nav items, user email, sign-out button\n- **Tab System:** Each tab receives props `{ user, profile, setProfile, tasks, setTasks, showToast, loggedFetch, switchTab, activeTheme, setActiveTheme }`\n- **Voice FAB:** Bottom-right floating button (Web Speech API) — 80px clearance required\n- **Mobile:** Bottom nav (primary 4 tabs) + More drawer\n\n**Tab Imports:**\n```\nTabTasks, TabCheckin, TabFocus, TabCalendar, TabHabits, \nTabTagTeam, TabFinance, TabNutrition, TabProgress, TabGuide, TabSettings\n```\n\n**Key State:**\n- `user`: Supabase auth object\n- `profile`: Full profiles record\n- `tasks`: Array from tasks table\n- `activeTab`: String (tasks|checkin|focus|calendar|habits|tagteam|finance|nutrition|progress|guide|settings)\n- `voiceFabState`: 'idle'|'recording'|'processing'\n\n**Auth Pattern:**\n```javascript\nonAuthStateChange((event, session) => {\n  if (session) {\n    hasSession.current = true;\n    if (event === 'INITIAL_SESSION' || event === 'SIGNED_IN') {\n      fetchProfile(session.user.id);\n      fetchTasks(session.user.id);\n    }\n  } else if (event === 'SIGNED_OUT' && hasSession.current) {\n    router.push('/login');\n  }\n})\n```\n\n**Voice FAB Flow:**\n1. Click FAB → start Web Speech Recognition\n2. User speaks → transcript → POST `/api/voice/parse` → Claude parses intent\n3. Auto-creates task/bill with undo option\n4. Updates tasks list\n\n---\n\n## Key Takeaways for Development\n\n1. **Database:** The `profiles` table tracks coaching context (persona_blend, baseline_profile) which drives personalization in check-ins\n2. **Check-in API:** Dual-path system — fast \"next_move\" path vs. full conversation path with tools\n3. **Dashboard:** Modular tab architecture with clear data flow (dashboard.js ↔ tabs, no circular imports)\n4. **Lessons:** Many patterns are locked in (auth, memory compression, rate limiting) — don't refactor these\n5. **Tools:** Check-in AI can execute task/bill/budget operations directly via Anthropic tool_use"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"c92e3624-e3e3-45f1-ae19-e176495ae8ad","uuid":"891dc565-52bb-4dae-a7ed-121b448304db","timestamp":"2026-03-26T12:16:41.310Z","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"Read these files and summarize their key contents:\n1. /Users/ryanjohnson/Documents/focusbuddy-app/docs/TERMINAL_CONTEXT.md\n2. /Users/ryanjohnson/Documents/focusbuddy-app/PRIMER.md\n3. /Users/ryanjohnson/Documents/focusbuddy-app/tasks/lessons.md\n4. /Users/ryanjohnson/D